Package org.aoplib4j.gof.observer.internal

Package containing the internals of the implementation of the Observer pattern.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GofObserver Interface representing the Observer object from the Observer pattern ( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observer_pattern).
GofSubject Interface representing the Subject from the Observer pattern( http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observer_pattern).
 

Class Summary
GofSubjectImpl Implementation of the GofSubject interface.
NotifyInformationImpl Object automatically created by the framework at the execution of the methods annotated with NotifyObservers and passed as parameter to the method ObserverCallback.notifyObserver( NotifyInformation).
ObserverAspect The AspectJ aspect implementing the Observer pattern.
 

Package org.aoplib4j.gof.observer.internal Description

Package containing the internals of the implementation of the Observer pattern.
Don't use into your project the classes from this package.
